 \text{trace} T = \sum_{r,s} ((e_i e_j^T e_r e_s^T e_k e_l^T))_{r,s}  = \sum_{r,s} \delta_{ir} \delta_{jr} \delta_{sk} \delta_{ls} = \delta_{ij} \delta_{kl} = \text{trace}(e_i e_j^T) \text{trace}(e_k e_l^T) 
